---
/**
 * Italic emphasized core-definition line.  Typical placement: inside a
 * `tone="tan"` or `tone="paper-sunk"` band between the hero and the
 * compare/detail bands.  Signals "this is the crystallized one-liner
 * that everything else elaborates on".
 */
---
<p class="core-def"><slot /></p>
<style>
  .core-def {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-han-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.2vw, 1.25rem);
    line-height: 1.5;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
</style>
